remain in misery,

00:24:26.760 --> 00:24:28.470 align:middle line:84%
and the misery
will go on growing.

00:24:28.470 --> 00:24:31.370 align:middle line:90%


00:24:31.370 --> 00:24:34.640 align:middle line:84%
As we become more
and more oblivious

00:24:34.640 --> 00:24:37.820 align:middle line:84%
of the existence
of the heart, we

00:24:37.820 --> 00:24:41.480 align:middle line:90%
become more and more miserable.

00:24:41.480 --> 00:24:44.390 align:middle line:84%
We are creating hell
on Earth, and we will

00:24:44.390 --> 00:24:47.330 align:middle line:90%
create more and more of it.

00:24:47.330 --> 00:24:51.830 align:middle line:90%
Paradise belongs to the heart.

00:24:51.830 --> 00:24:55.050 align:middle line:90%


00:24:55.050 --> 00:24:58.940 align:middle line:84%
