completely forgotten,"

00:25:02.070 --> 00:25:07.080 align:middle line:84%
thus, as I would put
it, has lost its impact

00:25:07.080 --> 00:25:11.090 align:middle line:84%
on human perception, thus human
behavior, thus human society.

00:25:11.090 --> 00:25:16.500 align:middle line:84%
"Nobody understands
that language anymore.

00:25:16.500 --> 00:25:22.740 align:middle line:84%
We understand logic, we
don't understand love.

00:25:22.740 --> 00:25:28.200 align:middle line:84%
We understand mathematics,
we don't understand music.

00:25:28.200 --> 00:25:30.690 align:middle line:84%
We become more and more
accustomed to the ways

00:25:30.690 --> 00:25:33.120 align:middle line:84%
