are different states often--

00:26:12.560 --> 00:26:14.060 align:middle line:90%
not least the head--

00:26:14.060 --> 00:26:16.770 align:middle line:90%
of ignorance.

00:26:16.770 --> 00:26:20.670 align:middle line:84%
And I can tell you my own
experience in relation to this.

