It's and an incredible
way of living your life,

00:26:51.550 --> 00:26:53.660 align:middle line:90%
in my experience, anyway.

00:26:53.660 --> 00:26:54.940 align:middle line:90%
It brings joy.

00:26:54.940 --> 00:27:01.230 align:middle line:84%
And it brings what
we call achievement.

00:27:01.230 --> 00:27:07.590 align:middle line:10%
Because this knows, and
it will guide you always

00:27:07.590 --> 00:27:11.850 align:middle line:10%
